---
title: Nan's Creamy Chicken Fettuccine with Parmesan & Hidden Leek
description: This saucy creation uses a creamy tomato sauce to coat linguine, with chunks of tender chicken and flavoursome Parmesan. Add thinly sliced leek that melts into the sauce and baby spinach that gently wilts when tossed with the pasta, and you’ve got a new recipe that's sure to please everyone.

*We've replaced the
fettuccine in this recipe
with spaghetti due
to local ingredient
availability. It'll be just
as delicious, just follow
your recipe card!*
